snippet.title: Zorus Official Trailer
snippet.description:
This game is about Zorus, where the fauna and flora are special in some ways. When we investigate this new world.

A beta version of a short game that last more than two minutes. Where we controlled Saina in a horizontal shot.


You can check this game in:

PlayStore: 
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.PickMG.Zorus

Itch.io:
https://martin-ao.itch.io/zorus

You can contact me in my social media
